Package serverSide.sharedRegions

Class Playground

  • java.lang.Object
    • serverSide.sharedRegions.Playground
  • public class Playground
extends java.lang.Object
    Playground. It is responsible for handling playground-related actions during the rope game. It is implemented as an implicit monitor. All public methods are executed in mutual exclusion. There are no internal synchronization points.
